                    <p>追觅去年 12 月推出 Air Power 17 磁吸移动充电宝，主打 15W Qi2 磁吸充电。</p><p>5000mAh 8mm 123g，官方定价 219 元。</p><p>按下方步骤下单，88VIP 凑单后可使用 200-25 元消费券，充电宝实付 151.4 元，评价晒单再返 20 元（详询客服），折合 131.4 元清仓好价。</p><p>下方两款加入购物车，一起付款结算即可：</p><ul class=" list-paddingleft-2"><li><p>点击下方卡片后 → 点击淘宝 App 右上角三个点“<span class="font-color-orangered"><strong>…</strong></span>” → 点击弹出页面右下角<strong><span class="font-color-orangered">淘金币</span> </strong>→ 下单付款；</p></li></ul><dir class=""><a contenteditable="false" href="https://uland.taobao.com/coupon/edetail?traceId=213e04d117794358578481339e0cc2&amp;srItem=1&amp;e=JX4dZP4wT1WlhHvvyUNXZfh8CuWt5YH5OVuOuRD5gLJMmdsrkidbOWBzzpT26idJYffSRUaLRMnyJnvZaKAS9HyolRPgaGxcOgZTnJJVeYtQ0uUXJlu5kBM0Y1duTYB7aczA%2F1QRyMfyMW3eIAWKRa6LeGhgJY%2B%2FxrWOm542iF3mhpDhiQUdsCHDJFv4HWtFROW6jx6bXtds1cCq%2BnZmGkob9ZRYa9bbqpXc9vysLag2hHMFUUWA%2FQpvhuGuJemkhJFPgaJn9UCxv6%2BLvWntiLcZelJt%2BzjyLo5zui4BV4NEbnIHNDR%2Fgwo3tbp4cVxHt3NYtEDNfLOGSa16IWRN7GUFFgz3RBVH&amp;union_lens=lensId:TAPI@1779435857@212cb236_1500_19e4ea46819_70c5@01" target="_blank"><span class="card main-site"><span class="card-logo"><img height="800" src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2026/5/a5e13ab8-a49d-4743-aff6-6330dade02cb.png?x-bce-process=image/format,f_auto" title="追觅 Qi2 磁吸支架充电宝 219 → 131 元破冰新低，支持 iPhone 15W+ 手表充电" width="800" /></span><span class="card-info"><span class="card-title"><span class="mall-data">天猫</span><span class="card-name">追觅 磁吸 + 支架充电宝</span></span><span class="card-abstract"> 3C 认证 可上飞机</span><span class="card-controls"><span class="price">淘金币加购物车 1 件</span><span class="card-btn-deep">直达链接</span></span></span></span></a></dir><dir class=""><a contenteditable="false" href="https://uland.taobao.com/coupon/edetail?traceId=213e04d017794363666331355e0ba1&amp;srItem=1&amp;e=%2B1kNUvxPeqOlhHvvyUNXZfh8CuWt5YH5OVuOuRD5gLJMmdsrkidbOWBzzpT26idJhi7PCjxE0BlKOJ6A0HhO2M15Q1wRhyNfeaG%2BFRwFZsAifcGEnVBYHPjW8dJpq8K62mwCY5fS7rVrTdT7cgXf6jgYSYpxmYtMsb%2Bvi71p7YhlXymvoVZzQ3wF4r%2BZB3L66MC4imfMWi2Ywek19h0d0NQV3tBpdKHodxJgRmH6PTUPrRT%2FGlevScjzpj5joESeiqP6wveQFBWrBNRUyvxLON6rz8LSjDwvc04%2BAAYn%2Buj32D2Gqq%2BYKd1AiZ3nWhdYSUlH%2Bp1%2FbPZ%2BOHfs5nLQGA%3D%3D&amp;union_lens=lensId:TAPI@1779436366@2104fe53_146f_19e4eac2b66_21df@01" target="_blank"><span class="card main-site"><span class="card-logo"><img height="800" src="https://img.alicdn.com/i2/2928873800/O1CN01uqAdq81dwRkQjfmFA_!!2928873800.jpg" title="追觅 Qi2 磁吸支架充电宝 219 → 131 元破冰新低，支持 iPhone 15W+ 手表充电" width="800" /></span><span class="card-info"><span class="card-title"><span class="mall-data">天猫</span><span class="card-name">凑单品 下单后可立即退款</span></span><span class="card-abstract"></span><span class="card-controls"><span class="price">加购物车 1 件</span><span class="card-btn-deep">直达链接</span></span></span></span></a></dir><p>0.8cm 纤薄机身，第 3 代星河硅负极电池，15% 高含硅量。</p><p>磁吸 <a class="s_tag" href="https://iphone.ithome.com/" target="_blank">iPhone</a> 充电后，iPhone 里可以直接显示充电宝剩余电量。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img height="798" src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2026/2/b58aaa1f-1315-41d2-b526-4a4599b0826a.png?x-bce-process=image/format,f_auto" title="追觅 Qi2 磁吸支架充电宝 219 → 131 元破冰新低，支持 iPhone 15W+ 手表充电" width="880" /></p><p>背板 + 边框采用铝合金，磁吸面板采用 AG 玻璃：手感细腻，无俱钥匙、硬币刮蹭。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img height="673" src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2025/12/a6f77cad-8be6-4975-bb66-cd4ade7e7159.jpg?x-bce-process=image/format,f_auto" title="追觅 Qi2 磁吸支架充电宝 219 → 131 元破冰新低，支持 iPhone 15W+ 手表充电" width="1440" /></p><p>外观方面，该产品采用铝合金 + AG 玻璃材质，其中 5000mAh 版本厚度 0.8cm，重量 123g；10000mAh 版本厚度 1.28cm，重量 189g。产品背面带有可收纳支架，并印有追觅 Logo 字样，底部带有 LED 灯及 USB-C 接口。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img height="781" src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2026/3/fcf41191-df4a-484d-b6c1-22adcc1eb5c6.png?x-bce-process=image/format,f_auto" title="追觅 Qi2 磁吸支架充电宝 219 → 131 元破冰新低，支持 iPhone 15W+ 手表充电" width="877" /></p><p>功率方面，该产品无线充电方面支持 15W 输出，有线充电方面支持 20W 输出，同时可供双设备（有线 + 无线）同时充电。</p><p><a class="s_tag" href="https://www.ithome.com/" target="_blank">IT之家</a>附产品参数如下：</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img height="1604" src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2025/12/acb89fc9-9b88-4101-bf76-83282ef423fe.jpg?x-bce-process=image/format,f_auto" title="追觅 Qi2 磁吸支架充电宝 219 → 131 元破冰新低，支持 iPhone 15W+ 手表充电" width="922" /></p><p>按下方步骤下单，88VIP 凑单后可使用 200-25 元消费券，充电宝实付 151.4 元清仓好价。</p><p>下方两款加入购物车，一起付款结算即可：</p><dir class=""><a contenteditable="false" href="https://uland.taobao.com/coupon/edetail?traceId=213e04d117794358578481339e0cc2&amp;srItem=1&amp;e=JX4dZP4wT1WlhHvvyUNXZfh8CuWt5YH5OVuOuRD5gLJMmdsrkidbOWBzzpT26idJYffSRUaLRMnyJnvZaKAS9HyolRPgaGxcOgZTnJJVeYtQ0uUXJlu5kBM0Y1duTYB7aczA%2F1QRyMfyMW3eIAWKRa6LeGhgJY%2B%2FxrWOm542iF3mhpDhiQUdsCHDJFv4HWtFROW6jx6bXtds1cCq%2BnZmGkob9ZRYa9bbqpXc9vysLag2hHMFUUWA%2FQpvhuGuJemkhJFPgaJn9UCxv6%2BLvWntiLcZelJt%2BzjyLo5zui4BV4NEbnIHNDR%2Fgwo3tbp4cVxHt3NYtEDNfLOGSa16IWRN7GUFFgz3RBVH&amp;union_lens=lensId:TAPI@1779435857@212cb236_1500_19e4ea46819_70c5@01" target="_blank"><span class="card main-site"><span class="card-logo"><img height="800" src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2026/5/a5e13ab8-a49d-4743-aff6-6330dade02cb.png?x-bce-process=image/format,f_auto" title="追觅 Qi2 磁吸支架充电宝 219 → 131 元破冰新低，支持 iPhone 15W+ 手表充电" width="800" /></span><span class="card-info"><span class="card-title"><span class="mall-data">天猫</span><span class="card-name">追觅 磁吸 + 支架充电宝</span></span><span class="card-abstract"> 3C 认证 可上飞机</span><span class="card-controls"><span class="price">淘金币加购物车 1 件</span><span class="card-btn-deep">直达链接</span></span></span></span></a></dir><dir class=""><a contenteditable="false" href="https://uland.taobao.com/coupon/edetail?traceId=213e04d017794363666331355e0ba1&amp;srItem=1&amp;e=%2B1kNUvxPeqOlhHvvyUNXZfh8CuWt5YH5OVuOuRD5gLJMmdsrkidbOWBzzpT26idJhi7PCjxE0BlKOJ6A0HhO2M15Q1wRhyNfeaG%2BFRwFZsAifcGEnVBYHPjW8dJpq8K62mwCY5fS7rVrTdT7cgXf6jgYSYpxmYtMsb%2Bvi71p7YhlXymvoVZzQ3wF4r%2BZB3L66MC4imfMWi2Ywek19h0d0NQV3tBpdKHodxJgRmH6PTUPrRT%2FGlevScjzpj5joESeiqP6wveQFBWrBNRUy